    <p><span>Playtest sign-ups now available.</span>
      </p></div><div><p>Publisher <a title="Companies > Netflix [83 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/netflix">Netflix</a> and developer <a title="Companies > Spry Fox [8 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/spry-fox">Spry Fox</a> have <a href="https://spryfox.com/2025/03/19/announcing-spirit-crossing/" target="_blank">announced</a> <em><a title="Games > Spirit Crossing" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/spirit-crossing">Spirit Crossing</a></em>, a cozy <a title="Genres > Co-Op [243 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/multiplayer/co-op">cooperative</a> life <a title="Genres > Simulation [673 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/simulation">simulation game</a> for iOS and Android. Playtest sign-ups are available now via the <a href="https://playspiritcrossing.com/" target="_blank">official website</a>. <span id="more-951168"></span></p><p>“<em>Spirit Crossing</em> is a cozy, cooperative life-sim focused on friendship and community,” reads the description. “Journey to a world where you can decorate your home, build with your friends, ride on a Fluffalo train, or join a dance party and jam session.”</p><p>Watch the announcement trailer below.</p><h2><span>Announce Trailer</span></h2><p><iframe title="Spirit Crossing | Official Game Announcement | Netflix" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/RNGs3tLPaF0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
